extends layout

block vars
  - var title='Donate to support development'
  - var url='donate'

block content
  include mixins/recipes.jade
  +inner-header("Donate to support development")

  div.main-tutorial.inner-page
    div.container  
      div.row
        div.col-md-12
          h2 Thanks for wanting to help!

          p The Ethereum Foundation is a non-profit organization registered in Switzerland. You can 
            a(href='./foundation') read more about it on the foundation page
            | .

          p 
            strong The Foundationâ€™s mission 
            | is to promote and support research, development and education to bring decentralized protocols and tools to the world that empower developers to produce next generation decentralized applications and together build a more globally accessible, more free and more trustworthy Internet.

          p If you want to help us achieve these goals, here are ways you can do so.

          h3 Donate

          p 
            strong Donating is a helpful way to support the Foundation. 
            | We've set up a special contract account to handle all 
            strong Bitcoin and Ether donations. 
            | All funds received are visible on the blockchain for anyone to see.  

            img(src='images/unicorn.png', width='150').float-right

          p Also, donating might get you a unicorn. As a playful way to thank the donors, we created a token on the ethereum blockchain called the &ldquo;Unicorn.&rdquo;. Any donation over 2.014 ethers will trigger the creation of a brand new unicorn that will be automatically sent to the donor. The unicorn token can be used as any other token: it can be sent to friends or to other wallets and can be used with other ethereum contracts. Unicorns are fun tokens with no assigned value and you can watch your Unicorns through your Ethereum Wallet (

            a(href='#watch-the-contract') here&rsquo;s how 
            | ).

          p 
            strong BEFORE YOU DONATE
            |, we want to make sure you know a few important things.
            include:md content/donate-conditions.md

          h4 If you want to donate, the instructions will appear after you certify the legality of the funds.

          p
            form(name="illegal", method="post")
              div.input
                  span.label-black These funds are not illegal &nbsp; &nbsp;
                  input(type="checkbox", name="not_illegal" id="legal")

  div#donate_to.main-tutorial.inner-page.even
    div.container  
      div.row
        div.col-md-12.donate
          h4 FOR ETHER DONATIONS, THE SPECIAL ACCOUNT IS:
          div.identicon
          span.dapp-identicon(style="background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,')")

          h2 Foundation Tip Jar 
          h3 0xfB6916095ca1df60bB79Ce92cE3Ea74c37c5d359
          p.caption For information about larger donations,   
            a(href='mailto:donate@ethereum.org') contact us

          h4 FOR BITCOINS DONATIONS, THE SPECIAL ACCOUNT IS
          h3 
            a(href='https://blockchain.info/address/39BaMQCphFXyYAvcoGpeKtnptLJ9v6cdFY') 39BaMQCphFXyYAvcoGpeKtnptLJ9v6cdFY
          p.caption Bitcoin donations are unfortunately not eligible for unicorns.

  div.main-tutorial.inner-page.inner-tutorial
    div.container  
      div.row
        div.col-md-12
          include:md content/donate.md        
          a.button.small(href='https://github.com/ethereum/ethereum-org/edit/master/views/content/donate.md') Improve this page

        




          

